Cell["\<\
Functions useful for the quantum signal processing (QSP) approach to quantum \
linear system problems (QLSP).\
\>", "TechNoteCaption",
 CellID->1830341579,ExpressionUUID->"72f25a06-f80a-4b2d-8ec3-c93857eaf155"],

